<section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 pt-24 pb-24 md:pt-36 md:pb-32">
  <div class="eyebrow mb-6">NORA Foundation · Canon v0.1.0 · draft-rfc</div>
  <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl md:text-6xl leading-[1.08] tracking-tight text-ink-800 max-w-4xl">
    Verifiable reasoning you can <span class="text-cardinal-600">bring to court</span>.
  </h1>
  <p class="mt-8 max-w-2xl text-xl leading-relaxed text-ink-600">
    NORA publishes <strong>Canon</strong> — a public specification for the artifact an AI system issues when a claim has survived Witness, Findings, Refutation, and Seal. Any recipient can verify a Canon attestation without the issuer's cooperation.
  </p>

  <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
